{"article_id":"pbffa1eHsUD21Dkk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell is expected to allow an impeachment trial against President Donald Trump to go ahead ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"calling a vote","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to acquit him","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"after proceedings have run their course","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"rather than seeking to immediately dismiss the charges ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"some Republican senators say .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Acquittal , rather than a procedural vote","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to dismiss the articles of impeachment ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"would definitively clear the president of the charges","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"raised against him by Democrats","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and expected to be approved by the House of Representatives .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"It would `` make more sense '' to vote on the articles of impeachment","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"than it would to simply dismiss them ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Sen. John Cornyn , R-Texas , told CNN .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Dismissal requires a simple 51-vote majority ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and such a vote could end in a tie , with `` all the recriminations","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that would flow from that , ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Cornyn added","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"According to the Constitution ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"it would take 67 votes in the Senate","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to convict Trump","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"and remove him from office , a threshold","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that is unlikely to be reached .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"A second Republican senator ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"speaking to CNN on condition of anonymity ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"said","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"McConnell , R-Ky. , will not call a vote","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"to move on the articles of impeachment","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"unless he 's certain","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"he has at least 51 votes","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"lined up","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to end the trial .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"McConnell ca n't count on the vote of Vice President Mike Pence","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"to break a tie .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Pence , as president of the Senate , has the mandate","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"to break ties on legislation and nomination ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"but ca n't vote in an impeachment proceeding ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"according to a GOP legislative aide ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"because he 'd be replacing Trump","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"if he was removed from office .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Senate Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"according to The Washington Post ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"say","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"they favor a short , limited trial with no witnesses","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"followed by a quick vote","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"to acquit the president .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Under this plan , the trial would be held early next year ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"the Post reports .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"McConnell hinted at the acquittal strategy to reporters Tuesday ,","depth":3},{"id":49,"text":"when he said","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"the Senate has two choices","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"after it hears opening arguments from the House and Trump 's defense counsel .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Many Senate Republicans say","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"they trust McConnell 's judgment in this matter ,","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"Axios reported Thursday .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":109,"left":102,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":77,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":60,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":60,"left":59,"right":5,"relation